ExpSyntax.val: Trim({0,85})&' and (upper(CRED_NAME) like upper(' &ASCIIChr (39)&'%'&Trim({0,13})&'%'&ASCIIChr (39)&') OR upper(DEBT_NAME) like upper(' &ASCIIChr (39)&'%'&Trim({0,13})&'%'&ASCIIChr (39)&') )'

Trim({0,85})&' and (exists (select 1 from '&DbName('{82,12}'DSOURCE)&' rd where rd.RE_NUMMER = '&Trim(Str({0,14},'9'))& ' and rd.RE_ID = DEBT_RE_ID) or exists (select 1 from '&DbName('{82,12}'DSOURCE)&' rc where rc.RE_NUMMER = '&Trim(Str({0,14},'9'))& ' and rc.RE_ID = CRED_RE_ID))'

Trim({0,85})&' and (exists (select 1 from rekeningen rd where rd.RE_REKENING = ' &ASCIIChr (39)&Trim({0,15})&ASCIIChr (39)& ' and rd.RE_ID = DEBT_RE_ID) or exists (select 1 from rekeningen rc where rc.RE_REKENING = ' &ASCIIChr (39)&Trim({0,15})&ASCIIChr (39)& ' and rc.RE_ID = CRED_RE_ID))'

SQL_STMT_U.val: select 1 from payment_initiation pi, paym_init_status ps where pi.status = ps.id and ps.STATUS_TYPE > 1 and pi.CREATE_DATE < to_date(':1','YYYYMMDD') and rownum = 1
